{"lastModified":1774272346860,"uri":"c::8294912922::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nYour holidays with this brand new Lagoon 46, built in 2020, will be unforgettable.\nCome onboard the Catamaran Alice for a lifetime experience.\n\nFreedom and audacity, gentle lifestyle and innovation make Lagoon 46 the perfect choice for summer vacation.\n\nThe combination with our experienced permanent crew guarantees you will enjoy the greek hospitality in a tailored and unique sailing experience!","blueprint":{"name":"ALICE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a2181550-4792-11f0-958c-098d26bea1d9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a21926c0-4792-11f0-8705-8d3916b5fee5/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a2261f10-4792-11f0-a8c4-856714a667b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a25f5780-4792-11f0-a8c4-856714a667b2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a217c730-4792-11f0-958c-098d26bea1d9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a2175200-4792-11f0-958c-098d26bea1d9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a2155630-4792-11f0-958c-098d26bea1d9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a2269440-4792-11f0-958c-098d26bea1d9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a273a2d0-4792-11f0-8705-8d3916b5fee5/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a2177910-4792-11f0-8705-8d3916b5fee5/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc77bf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4b